('9','4','What is the role of DILG in local governance?','multiple_choice','[\"To regulate local elections\",\"To oversee the implementation of laws and policies at the local government level\",\"To provide funding for all local governments\",\"To conduct audits of local government offices\"]','To oversee the implementation of laws and policies at the local government level',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:31:54','2026-02-20 10:31:54'),
('10','4','Which of the following is a core function of the Administrative Assistant II in DILG-CAR?','multiple_choice','[\"Managing financial records\",\"Conducting research for policy proposals\",\"Providing clerical and administrative support\",\"Writing legal documents\"]','Providing clerical and administrative support',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:32:23','2026-02-20 10:32:23'),
('11','4','What does the abbreviation ‘CS’ stand for in the context of government employment eligibility?','multiple_choice','[\"Career Services\",\"Civil Service\",\"Civil Society\",\"Central Secretariat\"]','Civil Service',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:32:51','2026-02-20 10:32:51'),
('12','4','Which of the following is an essential skill for an Administrative Assistant II?','multiple_choice','[\"Negotiation skills\",\"Data entry and report generation\",\"Knowledge of local legislation\",\"Crisis management\"]','Data entry and report generation',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:33:11','2026-02-20 10:33:11'),
('13','4','What is the purpose of the Personal Data Sheet (PDS) in government applications?','multiple_choice','[\"To verify educational qualifications\",\"To outline a candidate\\u2019s work experience and training\",\"To confirm a candidate\\u2019s residency\",\"To document the applicant\'s family background\"]','To outline a candidate’s work experience and training',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:33:35','2026-02-20 10:33:35'),
('14','4','In handling office supplies, which is the most effective practice?','multiple_choice','[\"Inventorying supplies once a year\",\"Ordering supplies as needed without tracking\",\"Maintaining a regularly updated inventory and ordering supplies in advance\",\"Only ordering supplies during budget allocation periods\"]','Maintaining a regularly updated inventory and ordering supplies in advance',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:33:56','2026-02-20 10:33:56'),
('15','4','The Office of the Regional Director in DILG-CAR focuses on which of the following areas?','multiple_choice','[\"Enforcing national laws on the local level\",\"Conducting local elections\",\"Training local government units (LGUs)\",\"Providing health services to local communities\"]','Training local government units (LGUs)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:34:20','2026-02-20 10:34:20'),
('16','4','What is the significance of having “Four hours of relevant training” as a requirement for the position?','multiple_choice','[\"It guarantees that applicants are eligible for promotion\",\"It ensures the applicant has basic knowledge in administration or office tasks\",\"It certifies that the applicant has completed specific technical education\",\"It is a condition for applying for a higher position\"]','It ensures the applicant has basic knowledge in administration or office tasks',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:34:47','2026-02-20 10:34:47'),
('17','4','What is the proper way to organize and maintain an office filing system?','multiple_choice','[\"Using a digital-only system\",\"Storing documents randomly for easy access\",\"Categorizing files by date, subject, and urgency\",\"Storing all documents in one large folder\"]','Categorizing files by date, subject, and urgency',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:35:07','2026-02-20 10:35:07'),
('18','4','If you are assigned to prepare a report for the Regional Director, which of the following is the best approach?','multiple_choice','[\"Write the report in a detailed and lengthy format\",\"Keep the report concise, clear, and focused on key points\",\"Include personal opinions and suggestions\",\"Prepare the report using complex jargon to demonstrate expertise\"]','Keep the report concise, clear, and focused on key points',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-20 10:35:30','2026-02-20 10:35:30'),
